\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 His exterior is heavy -- coarse like a peasant's, his face, his beard, his flat hair, and his}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 coarse, clumsy figure, suggest an overfed, intemperate, and harsh innkeeper on the}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 highroad. His face is surly-looking and covered with blue veins, his eyes are little and his}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 nose is red. With his height and broad shoulders he has huge hands and feet; one would}
